Welcome to Hachimi! A cat-parenting habit app where pixel cats grow as you build habits.

- Adopt unique pixel cats with thousands of appearance combinations
- Focus timer with countdown and stopwatch modes
- AI-powered cat chat with personality-driven responses
- 163 achievements across 4 categories
- Daily check-in with coin rewards and accessory shop
- Smart reminders with 9 scheduling modes
- Works offline, syncs when connected
- Available in 5 languages
